ECHO   ‚Ä¢ If you removed the virtual environment, run START.bat to set up again
ECHO   ‚Ä¢ If you kept the venv, you can run the application normally
ECHO   ‚Ä¢ Run diagnostics ^(option 4 in START.bat^) to verify everything works
ECHO.
